OL,7,FThe court heard how the conman
OL,8,Fsplashed out on a luxury cars and
OL,9,Fholidays after posing as a fundraiser
OL,10,Ffor charities including BBC , The
OL,11,FChristie, and other charities.
OL,13,FLevi, of St Davids Road South,, even
OL,14,Fdressed up in a Pudsey Bear suit and
OL,15,Fproduced fake badges and marketing
OL,16,Fmaterial to make his scam appear
OL,17,Flegitimate.
OL,19,FWhen he was caught, he claimed he had
OL,20,Fmade his wealth through escorting, and
OL,21,Fwas lucky at casinos and bookies.
