OL,7,FHe was handed a Serious Crime
OL,8,FPrevention Order after he admitted
OL,9,Ffraud and money laundering at Crown
OL,10,FCourt. The order prohibits him from
OL,11,Fany fundraising activities for five
OL,12,Fyears - or risk being returned to
OL,13,Fprison.
OL,15,FNow, a regulator has warned
OL,16,Forganisations to take steps to ensure
OL,17,Ffundraising activitiesJcarried out in
OL,18,Ftheir name are "open, honest and
OL,19,Flegal", after this gang of collectors
OL,20,Fcheated charities out of more than
OL,21,F#500,000 intended for good causes.
