OL,4,Ccharities wants to 'carry on
OL,5,Cfundraising'
OL,7,FBut in emails to the BBC, following
OL,8,Fhis conviction, he said he enjoys
OL,9,Fraising money for good causes and
OL,10,F"fully intends" to fundraise again in
OL,11,Fthe future.
OL,13,F"I can make a grand a week," he told
OL,14,Fofficers upon his arrest.
OL,16,FIn reality, the court heard he
OL,17,Ftargeted supermarkets to make "bucket
OL,18,Fcollections" which had not been
OL,19,Fauthorised.
