OL,7,FDuring the police investigation into
OL,8,Fthe gang, Levi was asked to account
OL,9,Ffor the money he had spent as none of
OL,10,Fit had been declared to HMRC.
OL,12,FLevi said that he had been working as
OL,13,Fan escort but was too embarrassed to
OL,14,Fdeclare the money. He also said he had
OL,15,Finherited #100,000 from his father.
OL,17,FLevi was also asked about 196 cash
OL,18,Fdeposits totalling #47,835.55 which
OL,19,Fwere made to his Santander account
OL,20,Fbetween 2011 and 2017.
