OL,5,Cfundraising'
OL,7,FHe said he "can't remember at this
OL,8,Fmoment" where that cash had come from.
OL,10,FThe biggest loser was the BBC, whose
OL,11,FChildren in Need charity lost out on
OL,12,F#47,000 donated by kind-hearted
OL,13,Fmembers of the public.
OL,15,FIn an email exchange from behind bars,
OL,16,FLevi denied being a scammer and
OL,17,Fclaimed he and his six co-defendents
OL,18,Fsimply pocketed expenses for their
OL,19,Ffundraising activities - which "ran
OL,20,Finto thousands".
